data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is a true gem with a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless appeal. Nestled on almost a 1/4 acre, this property boasts a spacious backyard with a fenced-in POOL, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by newer paint and flooring. The cozy living room has a large brick fireplace that adds to the warmth of the space. The bedrooms are generously sized and have carpet that is less than a year old! See this home today!
